    <p>GM<em>config (by sizzle)
A lightweight, reusable, cross-browser graphical settings framework for inclusion in user scripts. 
<a href="https://github.com/sizzlemctwizzle/GM">https://github.com/sizzlemctwizzle/GM</a></em>config/wiki</p>

